item.title: CVE-2022-1644|2024-08-03T00:10:03.792Z -- unknown -- call%26book%20mobile%20bar
item.description: The Call&Book Mobile Bar WordPress plugin through 1.2.2 does not sanitize and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when unfiltered_html is disallowed.
